data.description: Welcome to 196 Harbor Crest Drive, a 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom double wide mobile home on 2.35 acres! Home will be sold in As-Is condition. Just over 2,000 square feet, the home and main living areas are spacious. The living room has a fireplace with stone-surround and views looking into the backyard. The kitchen is a good size, has white and stainless appliances, ample cabinetry, and butcher block countertops. The master bedroom is large with a walk-in closet and an en-suite with a double-sink vanity, shower, and garden tub. The laundry room has a washer and dryer that will convey. The additional bedrooms in the home are all a good size, each with their own closet. The additional full bathroom has a single sink and a tub/shower combo. The backyard is extremely private with a small firepit, and a storage shed. Home is located extremely close to Lake Greenwood. Convenient access to Greenwood and Laurens! A great opportunity to own a home with acreage, schedule your showing today. Call to schedule your showing today.
